{"tid":1429510,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人人都說服","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:50:46.000Z","uid":300849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75c91212edc5184d9dfce065c16abe5457002dac","tid":1429510,"uid":300849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"這是<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民意戰</span></strong>，<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攻心為上</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請保持<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">包容</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">謙虛[/purple</strong>]，伺機說服，神父都唔會說服唔到人信耶穌就鬧人阿媽。<br />\n藍絲的確係敵人，甚至係比政府更強大的敵人。要嘗試說服、拉攏，就算說服唔到，都唔好梟張、鬧人：<br />\n<br />\n如果係親人，破壞左關係就無得再有機會說服 （<span style=\"color: green;\">包容</span>）<br />\n如果係陌生人，起碼維持黃絲的形象，並等待對方失禮，公眾會有目共睹。（[purple]謙虛</span>）<br />\n<br />\nPS 30歲以下有大量黃絲，請說服 30-35 一群。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n正確的方法、路線、口號，就會兌換成民意。"},{"pid":"1c772cc438ff6a664024bdd413dcd91a560841e8","tid":1429510,"uid":129988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"借推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(文宣時間)係時候吸納廢老藍絲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}